Package: safir-sdk-core
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${cli:Depends}, python (>= 2.7.0)
Description: Distributed real-time system framework
 Safir SDK Core is a middleware and platform for creation of
 distributed soft real-time systems. It is Scalable, Reliable,
 Portable, and last but not least, it is Open!
 Safir SDK Core is based on modern architectural principles
 and has a solid foundation in more than 20 years of
 development of distributed systems at Saab AB.
 .
 This package contains the runtime for Safir SDK Core.

